.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, chestnut, fuchsia, grey, orange
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, dutch, indonesian, french, indian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-mirinda, mirinda, fanta, hot-chocolate
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pinkmaster, havana, ritmeester, bolivar, vegafina
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, goldhamster, hamster, pony
1. the thai is the person who likes fuchsia
2. the swedish is the owner of the goldhamster
3. the dutch is the person drinking fanta
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes grey
5. the person who likes chestnut is the person drinking almond-mirinda
6. the ritmeester-smoker is the owner of the mouse
7. the person who likes orange is the havana-smoker
8. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle
9. the french is on the far left
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla
11. the owner of the ponys is on the left or right of the havana-smoker
12. the pinkmaster-smoker is the person drinking lemonade
13. the indonesian is the bolivar-smoker
14. the french is on the left or right of the person who likes pink
15. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    orange	|     pink	|      fuchsia	|     chestnut	|     grey	|
| Nationality	|   french	|    dutch	|    thai	|    indonesian	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     chinchilla	|    pony	|     mouse	|     hamster	|      goldhamster	|
| Beverage	|    hot-chocolate	|     fanta	|     mirinda	|    almond-mirinda	|      lemonade	|
| Cigar		|   havana	|    vegafina	|  ritmeester	|    bolivar	|   pinkmaster	|
